   var currSeries = null;\n    var seriesId = 1;\n    var classId = 1;\n    var numStandingRows = 6;\n    var currSeason = null;\n\n    function buildTable() {\n        (function ($) {\n            try {\n                if (seriesId != 286 && seriesId != 1) {\n                    //$('#seriesHead li').removeClass('active');\n                }\n\n                var link_url = 'http://'+currSeries.series_url+'/standings/driver?season='+currSeason+'&class='+classId;\n                $('.standingsButton').empty();\n                $('.standingsButton').append('<a href=\"'+link_url+'\">See Full Standings &gt;&gt;</a>');\n                $('table.standings tbody').empty();\n                $('table.standings tbody').append('<tr><th>Position</th><th>Driver</th><th>MFG</th><th>Points</th></tr>');\n\n                var standings_sorted = []\n                $.each(standings[currSeason][seriesId][classId], function(key, value) {\n                    standings_sorted.push(value);\n                });\n                standings_sorted.sort(function(a, b) {\n                    if (parseInt(a.rank) != parseInt(b.rank)) {\n                        return (parseInt(a.rank) - parseInt(b.rank));\n                    }\n                    else {\n                        return (parseInt(a.row_order) - parseInt(b.row_order));\n                    }\n                });\n\n                var iStandingRow = 1;\n                $.each(standings_sorted, function() {\n                    if (this.logo != '') {\n                        oemlogo = '<img class=\"standings-manufacturer-logo\" src=\"'+this.logo+'\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-height: 43px; width: auto;\" />';\n                    }\n                    else {\n                        oemlogo = '';\n                    }\n\n                    $('table.standings tbody').append('<tr><td>'+this.rank+'</td><td>'+this.driver_name+'</td><td>'+oemlogo+'</td><td>'+this.total+'</td></tr>');\n                    if (iStandingRow == numStandingRows) {\n                        return false;\n                    }\n                    iStandingRow++;\n                });\n            }\n            catch(err) {\n                //alert(err);\n            }\n        }(jQuery));\n    }\n\n    function bindSeriesList() {\n        (function ($) {\n            try {\n                $('#seriesHead li:first').addClass(getStandingsClassLogo(1));\n                $('#standingSeries ul').empty();\n                $.each(seriesclasses, function() {\n                    if (parseInt(this.id) != 286) {\n                        $('#standingSeries ul').append('<li value=\"'+this.id+'\">'+this.series_name+'</li>');\n\n                        if (parseInt(this.id) == seriesId) {\n                            currSeries = this;\n                            classId = parseInt(this.series_classes[0].class_id);\n                            $('#standings-current-series').html(this.series_name);\n                            $('#standings-current-class').html(this.series_classes[0].class_name);\n                            $('.standingsSeriesLogo').html('<img src=\"'+currSeries.series_logo+'\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100px; height: auto;\" />');\n                        }\n                    }\n                });\n\n                $('#seriesHead li').click(function() {\n                    seriesId = parseInt(this.value);\n                    $('#seriesHead li').removeClass('active');\n                    $(this).addClass('active');\n                    // get selected series and populate things\n                    $.each(seriesclasses, function() {\n                        if (parseInt(this.id) == seriesId) {\n                            currSeries = this;\n                            classId = currSeries.series_classes[0].class_id;\n                            $('#standings-current-series').html(currSeries.series_name);\n                            $('#standings-current-class').html(currSeries.series_classes[0].class_name);\n                            $('.standingsSeriesLogo').html('<img src=\"'+currSeries.series_logo+'\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100px; height: auto;\" />');\n                        }\n                    });\n                    bindClassList();\n                });\n\n                $('#standingSeries ul li').click(function() {\n                    seriesId = parseInt(this.value);\n\n                    $('#seriesHead li').removeClass('active');\n                    $('#seriesHead li:first').removeClass('pointStandingsChampionship pointStandingsChallenge pointStandingsLites pointStandingsPorscheUSA pointStandingsPorscheCanada');\n                    $('#seriesHead li:first').addClass('active');\n                    $('#seriesHead li:first').addClass(getStandingsClassLogo(seriesId));\n\n                    // get selected series and populate things\n                    $.each(seriesclasses, function() {\n                        if (parseInt(this.id) == seriesId) {\n                            currSeries = this;\n                            classId = parseInt(currSeries.series_classes[0].class_id);\n                            $('#standings-current-series').html(currSeries.series_name);\n                            $('#standings-current-class').html(currSeries.series_classes[0].class_name);\n                            $('.standingsSeriesLogo').html('<img src=\"'+currSeries.series_logo+'\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100px; height: auto;\" />');\n\n                        }\n                    });\n                    bindClassList();\n                });\n                bindClassList();\n            }\n            catch(err) {\n\n            }\n        }(jQuery));\n    }\n\n    function bindClassList() {\n        (function ($) {\n            try {\n                $('#standingClass ul').empty();\n\n\n\n                var classes_sorted = []\n                $.each(currSeries.series_classes, function(key, value) {\n                    classes_sorted.push(value);\n                });\n                classes_sorted.sort(function(a, b) {\n                    return parseInt(a.sort_order) - parseInt(b.sort_order);\n                });\n\n\n\n                $.each(classes_sorted, function() {\n                    $('#standingClass ul').append('<li value=\"'+this.class_id+'\">'+this.class_name+'</li>');\n                });\n\n                $('#standingClass ul li').click(function() {\n                    classId = parseInt(this.value);\n                    $('#standings-current-class').html($(this).html());\n                    buildTable();\n                });\n                buildTable();\n            }\n            catch(err) {\n\n            }\n        }(jQuery));\n    }\n\n    function bindSeasonList() {\n        (function ($) {\n            try {\n                $('#standingSeason ul').empty();\n\n                $.each(standings, function(season, seasonarr) {\n                    $('#standingSeason ul').append('<li value=\"'+season+'\">'+season+'</li>');\n                    currSeason = season;\n                });\n                $('#standings-current-season').html(currSeason);\n\n                $('#standingSeason ul li').click(function() {\n                    currSeason = parseInt(this.value);\n                    $('#standings-current-season').html(currSeason);\n                    buildTable();\n                });\n                bindSeriesList();\n            }\n            catch(err) {\n\n            }\n        }(jQuery));\n\n    }\n\n    function getStandingsClassLogo(iSeries) {\n        switch (iSeries) {\n            case 1:\n                return 'pointStandingsChampionship';\n                break;\n            case 2:\n                return 'pointStandingsChallenge';\n                break;\n            case 3:\n                return 'pointStandingsLites';\n                break;\n            case 4:\n                return 'pointStandingsPorscheUSA';\n                break;\n            case 5:\n                return 'pointStandingsPorscheCanada';\n                break;\n        }\n    }\n\n    (function ($) {\n
